Class AbstractPropertyModel<T>

java.lang.Object
  fr.n7.saceca.u3du.model.ai.object.properties.AbstractPropertyModel<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the modeled property, for instance Integer, Boolean, etc.
All Implemented Interfaces:
PropertyModel<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractNumericPropertyModel, BooleanPropertyModel, EnumPropertyModel, StringPropertyModel
public abstract class AbstractPropertyModel<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements PropertyModel<T>

An abstract common PropertyModel implementation, dealing with the following common properties of the modeled parameter:

  • Type (runtime accessible yet the interface is generic);
  • Name;
  • Default value;
  • Visibility.

Author:
Sylvain Cambon
